{"tid":2109361,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"水上列車？陸洪水1小時漲1米變平行鐵軌　網驚呼：千與千尋","createTime":"2020-07-15T07:54:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-15T23:56:39.000Z","uid":35519,"like":288,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":94,"replies":[{"pid":"7444b2c0613bef27768780ad217b3a0351037fd9","tid":2109361,"uid":35519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T07:54:15.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"x-large\"><strong>水上列車？陸洪水1小時漲1米變平行鐵軌<br />\n網驚呼：千與千尋</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bzCDxTd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbzCDxTd.png&h=7ad699da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xsjFMde.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxsjFMde.png&h=f873a45d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中國自6月下連日暴雨，導致三峽大壩水位不斷飆漲、突破150公尺高外，還讓下游的江西鄱陽湖水位突破歷史新高，許多省份都出現洪災。有中國網紅在YouTube上分享江西鄱陽縣的現況，由於當地溪水1小時內暴漲1公尺，不但淹沒3層樓高的民宅，連高鐵鐵軌都和水面平行，網紅說：「有種坐船的感覺」，這樣的景像讓網友覺得像動畫千與千尋、海賊王中的水上列車，紛紛表示，經典畫面再現。<br />\n<br />\n從畫面中可以看到，江西有部分地區被洪水淹沒，當地得居民被迫帶著簡便的隨身行李，離開家園；災情嚴重的地區連3樓民宅都泡在水裡，許多家具、電器都浮在水面上，隨著洪水不斷暴漲，連高鐵鐵軌都和水面平行，網紅說：「在火車上，有種坐船的感覺」。<br />\n<br />\n有人將網紅的影片分享到PTT上並說：「鄱陽湖因為破歷史水位，江西鄱陽縣的高鐵鐵軌，基本上已經跟水面持平了，簡直就跟海賊王裡面的海上列車一樣偉大，有沒有中國又創造一項不可能的八卦」、「這次災情真的很嚴重，但是還是有小粉紅說沒事，沒有比98年大洪水危險，真的是很樂觀」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pyaBjy0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpyaBjy0.jpg&h=a06b43f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AEQBjyL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAEQBjyL.jpg&h=e4a7003f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有網友覺得景像神似千與千尋、海賊王中的水上列車「神隱少女的橋段，好美！」、「神隱少女的經典畫面再現」、「東方威尼斯耶！」、「水之七島，有救了！」也有其他網友持不同的看法「沒事兒沒事兒，黨說沒事就是沒事」、「水很快就退了，沒事兒」、「竟然沒停駛，而且還有人敢搭，厲害了」、「火車還在開不就表示沒事兒？緊張啥？」。<br />\n<br />\n▼大撤離：九江市某鎮轉移大部分居民|下游村民撈電器和食物（影片來自YouTube－無修飾的中國頻道，若遭移除請見諒）<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FvZhZC5-baQ&amp;feature=emb_title\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DFvZhZC5-baQ%26feature%3Demb_title&d=Qf9F%2BOyPnpVTj1ufbg5Gu%2FSletu%2BpyBbwtETYsduqsw%3D&h=f3909532\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FvZhZC5-baQ&amp;feature=emb_title</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=779129\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D779129&d=Qf9F%2BOyPnpVTj1ufbg5Gu%2FSletu%2BpyBbwtETYsduqsw%3D&h=a6a2d002\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D779129&h=9c25cea4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=779129</a>"},{"pid":"cd1c5ac7d560a890e5bf2108cf3ad4628e744e10","tid":2109361,"uid":8308,"like":96,"dislike":2,"score":94,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T08:11:26.000Z","msg":"又有新景點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11454be6eb243ff5d4772c59cf9d19c4ce570cc7","tid":2109361,"uid":28068,"like":173,"dislike":1,"score":172,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T08:13:24.000Z","msg":"一小時成個湖要升一米<br />\n個水量要幾誇張<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca49eafdc32beb5da2418b96f69994347596e9fe","tid":2109361,"uid":343643,"like":61,"dislike":1,"score":60,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T08:16:42.000Z","msg":"宮崎駿搭時光機去支那取景晝千與千尋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86810b47e5efe73047df4d7aae34719594a4c54a","tid":2109361,"uid":22622,"like":70,"dislike":0,"score":70,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T08:17:40.000Z","msg":"大膽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n明明係坐緊船，亂噏嘢<br />\n想引導市民憎恨政府？犯國安法！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又拉得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94ad9e09a023fa7f95a95ccdf4beaaed8534a7a2","tid":2109361,"uid":276273,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T08:17:58.000Z","msg":"keep 住落去，做遊覽景點，<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee633546047d09ca35329e8857dfd0fcf5177862","tid":2109361,"uid":53062,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T08:19:31.000Z","msg":"東方威尼斯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5e24b145143b43c60355a3f5c707c0ebf41a70b","tid":2109361,"uid":293344,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T08:20:07.000Z","msg":"国安法嚴重漏洞<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2108532\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2108532</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"7e41192b3bb87bdb1df22bc7656bfb1decd364cd","tid":2109361,"uid":78304,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T08:28:46.000Z","msg":"水陸兩用高速列車<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好強，世界第一"},{"pid":"6f9525f5e42d826af85000994261c511681fb00c","tid":2109361,"uid":214129,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T08:31:21.000Z","msg":"又喪事當喜事辦，中國特色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7b58465a2a24cf65e0ff4274eb8ebfb7472f7a5","tid":2109361,"uid":342828,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T08:31:47.000Z","msg":"萬年難得一見嘅風景，即刻攪番個超值豪華團，回一回血先。"},{"pid":"e3848a275c804c46f162507e0da39e8da6127d96","tid":2109361,"uid":346701,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T08:32:28.000Z","msg":"新景點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n1:1還原千與千尋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78a7d29f522496f99bc1d5356a69f3d4605a5b95","tid":2109361,"uid":81140,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"